Package Shared

Class StudentEnrollment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.StudentEnrollment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class StudentEnrollment
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a StudentEnrollment in a Learning Platform Java application. The overall purpose of this class is to store information to display and send between the client and server, and to be used to keep track of which students are enrolled in which courses.
